Basic Tasks
[ ] @A Simple task with ID
[x] @B Completed task
[@] @C Ongoing work
[~] @D Obsolete item
[?] @E Questioned task
[!] @F Blocked task
[>] @G Delegated task
[*] @H In review task

Time Tracking
[ ] @TIME.1 ~2h Estimated 2 hours
[x] @TIME.2 :1.5h Took 1.5 hours
[@] @TIME.3 ~3h :2h In progress (2h of 3h done)
[ ] @TIME.4 ~30m Quick task
[ ] @TIME.5 ~2d Multi-day project

